des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your "Graywind Blinds". After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Graywind" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in "Graywind" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable "Graywind Smart" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Graywind Smart" login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, open the bedroom blinds."
"Alexa, close the bedroom blinds."
